values:
These past three weeks have been nothing short of amazing.&nbsp;
I've never smiled so much in 3 weeks ever.&nbsp; I kinda like it.
Hes wonderful.

Friends are pretty great too.&nbsp; They might be mostly guys but,&nbsp;
I dont think I would really want it any other way.
Some people don't really understand why I hang out with all of them,
and I don't expect them to.&nbsp; I love things the way they are right now.

I still miss Muskegon and friends&nbsp;I'd like to go back there soon,&nbsp;
really soon.

The 25th is coming faster then I had expected.&nbsp;
I can't wait till its all just over with and I can go back to&nbsp;
WORKING OUT! something i havent done in months

Life,&nbsp;
I love it..

this week has pretty much been nothing but mistakes for me
i can't go back and change anything&nbsp;
but if i could i would
i dont know how to tell someone how sorry i am
when i feel bad for what ive done or..
even embarressed for it&nbsp;
i want to hide and walk away even tho its prolly not good lol
when im mad or just hurt i cry..
it makes me feel like a little girl&nbsp;
but i dont know how else i can deal with it
when someone asks whats wrong or what happend etc.&nbsp;
i always choke up..i almost alway start crying and i try to hold back!&nbsp;
i try so effing hard not to just bawl my eyes out
when i know i made a mistake i get angry at that person sometimes
i dont know why i do...it always messes it up more..
i hate it when people dont accept my appoligy&nbsp;
it take so much out of me to even say it..
i have to think of how to say it so its meaningful&nbsp;
i know sometimes sorry doesnt cut it..but what do i do then?

i fee like everyone thinks im mean at lunch lol&nbsp;
i feel like ive become more...
forceful or maybe just not thinking twice before i do something
maybe what he said today i deserved
all i know is i was mostaly the fool&nbsp;
i made the mistake...
but i cant fix it but i would like to so bad
i would like to take back things i said
and maybe they dont care anymore
or forgot about it and that sucks
because i will sit here for weeks still remembering
and thinking how stupid i was..




sooo&nbsp;i guess&nbsp;i just think to much??&nbsp;
